markdownRemark.html:
It’s already midnight and I just finished my Node app and I’ll be sleeping soon, probably after writing this post.

Meet Mauch. My NodeJS app.

Mauch stands for Manga Update Checker. And I love giving names to my projects because they’re pretty recognizable.
